  stimulus_text = 'The author’s use of the phrase “a single, continuous line” is intended to suggest that there is a sense of unity and connection between the two seemingly disparate concepts of "nature" and "art." Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
